Package: genepicoloc
Title: R Package to Facilitate Genetic Colocalization Analyses
Version: 0.9.4
Date: 2026-03-22
Authors@R:
    person("Oleg", "Borisov", , "oleg.borisov@uniklinik-freiburg.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8700-4335"))
Description: Scalable genetic colocalization analysis across molecular and
    clinical trait datasets. Includes standalone implementation of the
    approximate Bayes factor (ABF) colocalization method, preprocessing
    tools (liftOver, variant naming, allele harmonization), and integration
    with public resources (eQTL Catalogue, GWAS Catalog). Designed for
    large-scale analyses with tar-based storage and parallel processing.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
